\ FORTHX16 - PSG TONE DEMO
\ PLAYS A SUSTAINED TWO-NOTE TONE ON THE VERA PSG.
\ REQUIRES THE X16 BUILD AND AUDIO ENABLED IN THE EMULATOR.
\ RUN WITH:  INCLUDE X16TONE.FTH

DECIMAL

\ PSGWAV ( WAVEFORM VOICE -- )   0=PULSE 1=SAW 2=TRIANGLE 3=NOISE
\ PSGFREQ ( FREQ VOICE -- )      FREQ WORD; HZ ~= FREQ * 0.745
\ PSGVOL ( VOL VOICE -- )        0..63, LEFT+RIGHT

0 0 PSGWAV   1000 0 PSGFREQ   60 0 PSGVOL     \ VOICE 0 ~ 745 HZ
0 1 PSGWAV   1500 1 PSGFREQ   50 1 PSGVOL     \ VOICE 1 A FIFTH ABOVE

CR S" PSG TONE PLAYING - SILENCE WITH:  0 0 PSGVOL  0 1 PSGVOL" TYPE CR
